com.teaminternational.coe.utils

Class PropertiesContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teaminternational.coe.utils.PropertiesContext

  • public class PropertiesContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Properties Context Class. Used in whole projects to get config of all used systems from *.properties files in /resources folder.
    Loads list of properties from resources folder to be available in system in singleton manner.
    Available upgrades:
    Update to use overridden properties located in external folder;
    Add more ui properties files to divide parts of application.
    Version:
    1.0 01/10/18
    Author:
    Vladyslav.Yegorov@teaminternational.com
